steps.message:
Remember:
1) **[accent]analyzing statements[/accent]** is key to winning the debate as it gives you Insight Points and it may also unlock bonus statements, 
2) Once you gather **[accent]enough Insights[/accent]**, you can **[accent]get help to reveal which sentences hide fallacies[/accent]**; 
3) Choosing the best statement will **[accent]influence the Moderator's favour[/accent]**;
4) **[accent]unlocked bonus statements[/accent]** are **[accent]usually more effective[/accent]** than regular statements.
